Package: climasus.data
Title: Shared Metadata Catalog for CLIMA-SUS Packages
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Max", "Anjos", email = "maxanjos@campus.ul.pt",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5765-5838"))
    )
Description: Provides access to the shared JSON metadata catalog used by
    climasus4r and climasus4py, including disease group classifications,
    geographic codes, data dictionaries, and SUS system metadata. All data
    files are bundled in inst/extdata/ and accessed via helper functions.
